<paragraph blockId="7.[136,1452,1169,1987]" pageId="7" pageNumber="64">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[189,356,1925,1951]" pageId="7" pageNumber="64">Etymology:—</emphasis>
Named in honour of Ing. Agr. Mario Esteban Véliz Pérez (1964–), Coordinator-curator of the BIGU Herbarium, who has contributed substantially to the knowledge of the flora of 
<collectingCountry box="[1091,1216,1961,1987]" name="Guatemala" pageId="7" pageNumber="64">Guatemala</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
